<template>
  <a-card>
    <project-table
      title="规模"
      :getListFn="projectAPI.getScaleList">
    </project-table>
    <project-table
      title="性质"
      :getListFn="projectAPI.getPropertyList">
    </project-table>
    <project-table
      title="用途"
      :getListFn="projectAPI.getPurposeList">
    </project-table>
    <project-table
      title="资金来源"
      :getListFn="projectAPI.getFundSourcesList">
    </project-table>
    <project-table
      title="结构形式"
      :getListFn="projectAPI.getStyleList">
    </project-table>
  </a-card>
</template>

<script>
  import projectAPI from '../../api/project'
  import ProjectTable from './components/ProjectTable'

  export default {
    name: 'Project',
    components: {
      ProjectTable
    },
    data () {
      return {
        projectAPI
      }
    },
    methods: {}
  }
</script>

<style scoped lang="less">
  .ant-divider-inner-text {
    font-size: 20px !important;
  }
</style>
